{"tid":18218,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"綁兩女掠獨立屋　堂兄弟判囚","createTime":"2016-12-02T07:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T07:37:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e38150aaaf074ca4ee3a4cd47c4da3031475eda","tid":18218,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T07:12:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161202/19852720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161202%2F19852720&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXRpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=b3e4ad3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161202%2F19852720&h=7885f147\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161202/19852720</a><br />\n<br />\n綁兩女掠獨立屋　堂兄弟判囚<br />\n<br />\n4,399<br />\n ■次被告（戴帽者）案發後攀到樹上躲藏，其後被勸服返回地面。<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n■次被告（戴帽者）案發後攀到樹上躲藏，其後被勸服返回地面。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】來自貴州的一對堂兄弟聲稱獲邀來港打工，卻被人帶往西貢一所獨立屋行劫，趁女戶主返家時強行入屋，將女戶主及菲籍女傭綁起，連同屋內一名歲半幼童推入廁所，繼而大肆搜掠約30萬元財物後離去。堂兄弟昨在高院承認搶劫罪，被判囚5年4個月。辯方求情時一度指被告於犯案過程中善待事主，法官陳慶偉即反駁「唔可以用善待喎」，辯方遂謂「我講善待嗰陣係有個引號括住嘅」。<br />\n28歲被告魯再發及33歲魯再云於去年12月15日連同另一身份不詳人士在大網仔路雅都花園獨立屋犯案，事後女戶主及菲傭自行鬆綁報警。警方稍後分別在西貢碼頭附近及大網仔路一棵樹上截獲被告。<br />\n官指經小心策劃<br />\n二人早前曾向法庭表示，現時仍在逃的主謀當日威脅他們合作，否則要他們游泳回內地，惟昨日均撤回有關說法。<br />\n陳官指被告等人在內地買刀具及辣椒水等，繼而來港犯案，明顯經小心策劃。<br />\n被告另被控非法入境罪，因法例所限，高院未能一併判刑，要交由裁判法院處理，陳官希望控方向律政司反映，能否修例免浪費資源及時間。<br />\n案件編號：HCCC248/16<br />\n■記者楊家樂  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n轉介卧底警公屋墮胎　女中醫候判<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n已婚司機狎13歲女網友"},{"pid":"dc1c3ce3b4d9c1fe1d093c35841d9fbb453cc1d4","tid":18218,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T07:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161202/large/02ls3p4new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161202%2Flarge%2F02ls3p4new.jpg&h=0ebf2c35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4be4084f943d32f18de75ed3d087ff1b6f738d60","tid":18218,"uid":8198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T07:19:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161202/large/02ls3p4new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161202%2Flarge%2F02ls3p4new.jpg&h=0ebf2c35&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲拎住鑵可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced573bfbc666cea23f9a4d734d2f447cbcf17f9","tid":18218,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T07:21:10.000Z","msg":"咁有義氣唔篤埋果條友出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b30d76724b506f36997a9d7747dd7b2ae6824c7","tid":18218,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T07:22:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161202/large/02ls3p4new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161202%2Flarge%2F02ls3p4new.jpg&h=0ebf2c35&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲拎住鑵可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/250pix/20021106/Article_ent/06ec1p8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F250pix%2F20021106%2FArticle_ent%2F06ec1p8.jpg&h=e0ade64b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i2.sinaimg.cn/ent/2013/1218/U8551P28DT20131218142502.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi2.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2F2013%2F1218%2FU8551P28DT20131218142502.jpg&h=dd92d9f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e06ac35011674c3be765c653ad600f9450d21713",